metadata.name: Labyrinth
metadata.description:
I think life is like walking in a labyrinth
There are many paths to choose from
Each path has many intersections
The path you choose may be the right one
Or maybe it's the wrong path
You never know until you hit a dead end
It can be a rough and time-consuming journey
Or maybe it's a shorter and smoother way to reach the exit
Many people are lost in a labyrinth their whole lives
Just to wait for the light at the end
to lead us out of this labyrinth
